title: Patients plasma exosomal miRNA [N1]
extract_protocol_ch1: Total RNA of plasma exosomes was using Qiazol and RNeasy Minelute spin column following the manufacturer’s user guide.RNA concentration was determined using Nanodrop. The content and quality of exosomal RNAs were determined using the 2100 Bioanalyzer instrument.
extract_protocol_ch1.1: RNA libraries were prepared for sequencing using standard Illumina protocols
data_processing: We use AASRA  to map clean reads to reference genome and other sRNA database, except Rfam which was performanced by using cmsearch
data_processing.2: Supplementary_files_format_and_content: RPKM-NB-exomalmiRNA.xls file includes RPKM values
